title: LF Someone to help me Improve.
body:
I am a Support Main looking to improve. I guess I'm looking for a coach in a sense, but I sadly do not have any money to offer. I want to get better so I can hit my goal of Diamond by the end of the year. I have discord and would really appreciate if I could even get just a couple of tips. Please add me if you would like to help me, and if not I understand. 

Thanks for Reading,
DramaticChicken

replies.body: Add me if you wanna play I got diamond friends who could give u a few tips
